解 香港大學 會有經濟日報股份<br />\n仲係四大股東"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"大股東捐出去"},{"pid":"ecb881899edc66650e0475b3c91709c797b13752","tid":1357042,"uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"73f6e9eb3d0505767751aa1a3aac984b0707a54d","tid":1357042,"uid":163017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9aba28c9eec3f82f8c0ae13700d4bb096a3731a","tid":1357042,"uid":37111,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"點解 香港大學 會有經濟日報股份<br />\n仲係四大股東"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:11:30.000Z","msg":"我仲google緊<br />\n新手唔係好識點查，有冇巴打會有頭緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"創辦《香港經濟日報》之前，馮先生與伙伴成功掌握 1970年代後期中國內地改革開放政策所帶來的商機，並在多個商業領域開展業務。<br />\n<br />\n馮先生在香港大學攻讀期間，活躍於學生活動，並於 1971年當選為香港大學學生會會長。1972年，馮先生於香港大學畢業，獲授社會科學學士學位，其後往英國曼徹斯特大學深造，於1977年獲頒經濟學文科碩士學位。<br />\n<br />\n為回饋母校和香港社會，馮先生偕同夫人於2006年，以兩人名義向香港大學捐贈了其名下經濟日報集團已發行股數百分之十的股份，用作成立「杜鵑 (1972) 基金」，以支持港大發展有利香港社會的項目。"},{"pid":"b352e7bdab0fe52c2a420f2e45dc7a7e530fda6a","tid":1357042,"uid":1581,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"鬼佬做野既爽手，死攬攬到公司攬炒為乜"},{"pid":"ae8e292738d1b5501529887075c2de837f404c97","tid":1357042,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"搜到一個<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bonbonlifestylewebazine.com/2019/07/23/arthur-shek-kang-chuen-resigns-as-ed-of-hket-0423/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbonbonlifestylewebazine.com%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2Farthur-shek-kang-chuen-resigns-as-ed-of-hket-0423%2F&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=0f1dc597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bonbonlifestylewebazine.com/2019/07/23/arthur-shek-kang-chuen-resigns-as-ed-of-hket-0423/</a>"},{"pid":"d5990d2076eb3b130085ab4cb8f4d28f79bcf062","tid":1357042,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy